Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 14:37:16 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add OpenTelemetry tracing instrumentation for sandbox
 controller
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Introduce a pluggable tracing framework with TraceEmitter interface,
allowing community (OTEL SDK) and internal (JSONL file) implementations
to share the same TraceOperation wrapper and phase constants.

Instrumented 6 Pod lifecycle phases in commonControl:
- CreatePod, DeletePod, PausePod, ResumePod, Patch, AgentRuntimeInit

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: 毓榕 <yurong.mh@alibaba-inc.com>
